HEADWORD: Trustful
<hw>Trust"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Full of
trust; trusting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Worthy of trust; faithful; trusty;
trustworthy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Trust"ful*ly</wf>,<pos>adv.</pos> --
